<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Reset Your Password</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #0D1117; color: #f0f6fc; padding: 20px;">

<div style="max-width: 600px; margin: auto; background-color: #151B23; border-radius: 8px; overflow: hidden;">

    <div style="background-color: #4CAF50; color: #ffffff; padding: 20px; text-align: center;">
        <h1 style="margin: 0; font-size: 24px;">Password Reset Request</h1>
    </div>

    <div style="padding: 20px; color: #f0f6fc;">
        <p>Hello,</p>

        <p>We received a request to reset your password for your Penny Wise account. Please click the button below to reset your password:</p>

        <div style="text-align: center; margin: 20px 0;">
            <a href="{{ url('app_reset_password', {token: resetToken.token}) }}" style="background-color: #4CAF50; color: #ffffff; padding: 12px 24px; border-radius: 5px; text-decoration: none; font-size: 16px;">Reset Password</a>
        </div>

        <p>If the button above doesnâ€™t work, you can copy and paste the link below into your browser:</p>
        <p style="word-break: break-all;"><a href="{{ url('app_reset_password', {token: resetToken.token}) }}" style="color: #4CAF50; text-decoration: underline;">{{ url('app_reset_password', {token: resetToken.token}) }}</a></p>

        <p><strong>Note:</strong> This link will expire in {{ resetToken.expirationMessageKey|trans(resetToken.expirationMessageData, 'ResetPasswordBundle') }}.</p>

        <p>If you did not request this, you can safely ignore this email.</p>

        <p>Thank you,<br>The Penny Wise Team</p>
    </div>

    <div style="background-color: #0D1117; padding: 15px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: #9198A0;">
        <p>Penny Wise Inc.</p>
        <p><a href="https://www.pennywise.com" style="color: #4CAF50; text-decoration: none;">www.pennywise.com</a></p>
    </div>

</div>
</body>
</html>
